FBIS4-38921 "drsov107_p_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-107 Daily Report 2 Jun 1994 CAUCASUS Armenia Vice President Leaves for United States Vice President Leaves for United States NC0206202794 Yerevan SNARK in English 1540 GMT 2 Jun 94 NC0206202794 Yerevan SNARK English BFN [Text] Yerevan, 2 June (SNARK) -- Today the Armenian Vice-President Gagik Arutunyan flew to France and USA, to discuss the issues related with All-Armenian Foundation "Hayastan" ("Armenia"). As SNARK reporter was told in the press bureau of Armenian President, Arutunyan will also attend the celebration of Hrayr Hovnanian, the chairman of "Armenian American Assembly" in New York. It has also become known to SNARK that Gagik Arutunyan has taken with him a video-address of Armenian President Levon Ter-Petrosyan to Armenian Diaspora in USA.
